      <title class="- topic/title ">For Windows</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
        <ol class="- topic/ol ">
          <li class="- topic/li ">Go to the <xref format="html" href="https://ffmpeg.org/download.html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref ">FFmpeg
               download web page</xref>.</li>
          <li class="- topic/li ">Download the package which is appropriate for your operating
            system.</li>
          <li class="- topic/li ">Add the path to the FFmpeg executable file to your PATH
            environment variable.</li>
          <li class="- topic/li ">Reactivate Katalon Studio for this installation to take
            effect.</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="- topic/p ">Click <xref format="html" href="http://blog.gregzaal.com/how-to-install-ffmpeg-on-windows/" scope="external" class="- topic/xref ">here</xref>
